main event: A vertical structure was reported emerging from a cloudy background in Emmons, Minnesota.
interesting points: The report was filed by Lt. Richard J. Emmons from the USAF., The sighting occurred on July 6, 1959., The report includes one photograph showing the structure., The photograph shows a tall and narrow vertical structure with no additional objects or subjects., The case number is 6420 and project number is 10062.
